@startuml
title Dispatcher Ordering + Fair-share + Coalesce Latest-wins

actor "Consumer A" as A
actor "Consumer B" as B
participant "Dispatcher" as D
queue "Data Bus" as Bus

D -> D : receive events (O,BTC,Trade)\nreorder seq_provider -> ingest_ts
D -> D : coalesce map for Ticker/Book/KlineSummary
D -> D : fair-share schedule A,B (token buckets)
D -> Bus : publish ev#101
Bus -> A : deliver ev#101
Bus -> B : deliver ev#101
D -> Bus : publish ev#102
Bus -> A : deliver ev#102
Bus -> B : deliver ev#102

note over D
- Never coalesce ExecReport (lossless).
- Coalesce only stateful latest-wins kinds.
end note
@enduml
